Package: datar
Title: handles saving and loading project data
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
  person(given='Christopher',
         family='Barrington',
         role=c('aut', 'cre'),
         email='christopher.barrington@crick.ac.uk',
         comment = c(ORCID='0000-0003-1281-2658'))
Description: Allows project data to be stored and accessed through `data()` and `system.file` functions outside of a package. Data is stored, by default, in the project root rather than the package which may be symlinked by `renv`.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
